n
 n!=n\cdot(n-1)!. 
 n!\frac{k}{k!}\frac{n-k}{(n-k)!}=n!\frac{k}{k(k-1)!}\frac{n-k}{(n-k)(n-k-1)!}=\frac{n!}{(k-1)!(n-k-1)!} 
\begin{align} k(n-k)\binom{n}{k}&=k(n-k)\frac{n!}{k!(n-k)!}\\  &=\frac{n!}{(k-1)!(n-k-1)!}\\  &=\frac{n(n-1)(n-2)!}{(k-1)!(n-k-1)!}\\  &= n(n-1)\binom{n-2}{k-1} \end{align}
 k!=k(k-1)!  
